<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ ABOUT ═══════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="about-grid reveal">
      <div class="about-text">
        <div class="section-label">Who We Are</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">WORLD-CLASS<br><span class="red">TAEKWON-DO</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Family-friendly ITF Taekwon-Do classes from age 3 to adult, across multiple locations throughout Scotland.</p>
        <p>Elite Scotland Taekwon-Do is more than a martial arts club — it's a community built on values that shape character and transform lives. Whether you're a complete beginner or looking to push to the next level, our structured classes cater to every stage of the journey.</p>
        <p>Every session is carefully designed to develop not just physical skill, but mental resilience, self-confidence, and discipline that carries into every aspect of life.</p>
        <a href="#" onclick="event.preventDefault();openModal('modal-trial')" class="btn-red" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">Start Your Journey Today</a>
      </div>
      <div class="instructor-card">
        <div class="instructor-badge">⚫ Head Instructor</div>
        <h3>Master Catherine Divine<span>8th Dan Black Belt</span></h3>
        <div class="rank-stars">
          <div class="rank-star"></div>
          <div class="rank-star"></div>
          <div class="rank-star"></div>
          <div class="rank-star"></div>
          <div class="rank-star"></div>
          <div class="rank-star"></div>
          <div class="rank-star"></div>
          <div class="rank-star"></div>
        </div>
        <p>One of Scotland's most respected ITF Taekwon-Do instructors, Master Divine brings decades of experience, international competition, and a genuine passion for developing students at every level — having represented Scotland at both European and World Championship level.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--off-white);"><span style="color:var(--red);">✓</span> International ITF certified</div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--off-white);"><span style="color:var(--red);">✓</span> European &amp; World Championship experience</div>
         
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════ BENEFITS ═══════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="benefits">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 0.5rem;">
      <div class="section-label" style="justify-content:center;">What You'll Gain</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">SIX PILLARS OF<br><span class="red">TAEKWON-DO</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <div class="benefit-card reveal"><div class="benefit-icon">🥊</div><h3>Self Defence</h3><p>Practical, effective techniques taught progressively. Learn to protect yourself and those around you with real confidence.</p></div>
      <div class="benefit-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.07s"><div class="benefit-icon">🏆</div><h3>Confidence</h3><p>Watch self-belief grow with every grade. Our students carry their confidence into school, work, and everyday life.</p></div>
      <div class="benefit-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.14s"><div class="benefit-icon">💪</div><h3>Fitness</h3><p>Full-body conditioning through dynamic kicking, striking, and pattern work. Better fitness as a natural result of enjoyable training.</p></div>
      <div class="benefit-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.21s"><div class="benefit-icon">🎯</div><h3>Discipline</h3><p>Structure and respect are woven into every class. Students learn to set goals, commit to training, and follow through.</p></div>
      <div class="benefit-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.28s"><div class="benefit-icon">🤝</div><h3>Respect</h3><p>A core tenet of Taekwon-Do. Students learn to treat instructors, peers, and themselves with genuine respect and humility.</p></div>
      <div class="benefit-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.35s"><div class="benefit-icon">🧠</div><h3>Focus</h3><p>Improved concentration and mental clarity. The patterns and techniques of Taekwon-Do train the mind as much as the body.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

