        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.6;">Technique videos covering kicks, stances, hand techniques and self-defence combinations. Watch anywhere, anytime.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--navy);border:1px solid rgba(200,16,46,0.2);border-radius:6px;padding:1.5rem;">
        <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🧘</div>
